prep for npm publish: release CI + fix test discovery

- move test/fixtures/fake-mcp-server.mjs -> support/: node --test was
  auto-running the long-lived fixture (it matches **/test/**/*.mjs), which
  hung the suite for 15s then exited 1. node --test is now 98/98, exit 0.
- add .github/workflows (ci, publish, auto-release, codeql, npm-token-health),
  adapted from the @askalf sibling set for warden's zero-build JS.
- add package-lock.json (zero-dep) so `npm ci` is reproducible in CI.
- add CHANGELOG.md with the 0.2.0 release notes (auto-release reads it).
- point demo/mcp-smoke.mjs at the moved fixture.
